1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,800
[EP. 02] Before You and I Become we

2
00:00:04,900 --> 00:00:06,020
So, guys are

3
00:00:06,160 --> 00:00:08,180
not into childish girls?

4
00:00:08,260 --> 00:00:09,780
Yeah? Do guys prefer mature ones?

5
00:00:11,300 --> 00:00:12,600
Huh? Ha Eun!

6
00:00:12,720 --> 00:00:13,560
Yeo Reum! How are you?

7
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:17,200
What? That guy is Yeo Reum’s friend?

8
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:19,520
Yeon Woo, this is Ha Eun from my department.

9
00:00:20,340 --> 00:00:22,960
Ha Eun, this is my high school friend Yeon Woo.

10
00:00:23,220 --> 00:00:24,540
Yeah…I’ve seen him

11
00:00:24,540 --> 00:00:25,940
here and there.

12
00:00:25,940 --> 00:00:28,180
Oh, really? You two know each other?

13
00:00:28,340 --> 00:00:30,000
Yeon Woo, are you close to Ha Eun?

14
00:00:30,140 --> 00:00:31,660
She’s one of my best friends …

15
00:00:31,660 --> 00:00:32,340
Not really.

16
00:00:32,580 --> 00:00:33,080
Ah...

17
00:00:34,480 --> 00:00:36,400
huh...

18
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:40,060
Alright. Let’s toast! To celebrate we’re all here.

19
00:00:40,940 --> 00:00:42,640
Come on, clink clink!

20
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:44,180
Cheers!

21
00:00:45,220 --> 00:00:47,160
Why so much formality?

22
00:00:47,160 --> 00:00:49,040
Drop the honorifics, Ha Eun.

23
00:00:49,180 --> 00:00:50,320
Should…I?

24
00:00:50,480 --> 00:00:52,340
Let’s toast to that then. Cheers!

25
00:00:53,060 --> 00:00:54,440
You’re getting drunk, Yeo Reum …

26
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:57,060
No, I’m not drunk yet. Cheers!

27
00:00:57,220 --> 00:00:58,700
Are you okay?

28
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:00,840
Of course, drink up! Cheers!

29
00:01:02,080 --> 00:01:05,240
Oh dear… Why is she drinking so much when she can’t take it?

30
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:07,060
Argh, so awkward…

31
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:10,140
Hey, why are you so drunk?

32
00:01:10,260 --> 00:01:11,360
Oh, it’s Wook! Wook!

33
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:13,040
She just kept going.

34
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:13,980
Just take her home.

35
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:15,100
ah...

36
00:01:15,180 --> 00:01:16,460
I wanna go home!

37
00:01:16,980 --> 00:01:18,120
Hey! Yeo Reum! Wait up!

38
00:01:18,260 --> 00:01:18,760
See you later guys!

39
00:01:25,700 --> 00:01:29,980
Feeling much closer thanks to Yeo Reum

40
00:01:33,500 --> 00:01:37,220
Romance, not so far yet not so close

41
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:40,860
Gun Ha, are you asleep?

42
00:01:41,020 --> 00:01:44,580
Gun Ha, are you busy?

43
00:01:45,340 --> 00:01:50,620
What are you up to?

44
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:55,260
He wouldn’t like it if I contacted him at this time …

45
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:59,480
Wook, I’m drunk….

46
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,960
What?

47
00:02:03,060 --> 00:02:09,640
A Day Before Us

